Bowie.Woodmore, Maryland: Woodmore is an unincorporated area and census-designated place (CDP 86710)  in Prince George's County, Maryland within the boundaries of Route 193 (Enterprise Road) to the west, Church Road to the east, Route 214 (Central Avenue) to the south and Route 50 to the north. Woodmore Road runs east and west through the center. The population of Woodmore (defined by CDP 86710) was 3,936 at the 2010 census.
